{% comment %}
  Champagne de Lossy — header intro reveal
  On page load the whole header group slides down from the top. Pure CSS
  animation (runs once on load). No fill-mode "forwards", so afterwards the
  header has no transform and the sticky header keeps working. Skipped for
  reduced-motion users; not rendered in the theme editor (see theme.liquid).
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    #header-group {
      animation: cdlHeaderDown 0.9s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.3s backwards;
    }

    @keyframes cdlHeaderDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-100%); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
  }
</style>
